        BUILD IT
      </span>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
        Your Personalized <br class="hidden md:block" />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary to-purple-500">
